'''宜家铅笔'''是[[宜家家居|宜家家居]]在全球门店为顾客免费提供的小型[[铅笔|铅笔]]。宜家铅笔以多样化的设计而闻名，最早设计为蓝色，后来变为黄色，而如今的宜家铅笔是纯木色。尽管外观颜色有所变化，但尺寸一直为直径 7 毫米，长 78 毫米 <ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.benito.nl/product/mini_potlood_(ikea_maat).html|title = Mini potlood (IKEA maat)|work = benito.nl|access-date = 2015-09-14|archive-date = 2014-10-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006072742/http://www.benito.nl/product/mini_potlood_%28ikea_maat%29.html}}</ref>。

仅在加拿大门店，宜家家居每年就需要订购 520 万支铅笔。<ref name="Toronto Star">{{Cite news|url = http://www.thestar.com/life/2010/12/22/a_penchant_for_pencils.html|title = A penchant for pencils|work = [[Toronto_Star|Toronto Star]]|date = 22 December 2010|accessdate = 11 November 2014|author = Cross, Allison|archive-date = 2021-08-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210830214704/https://www.thestar.com/life/2010/12/22/a_penchant_for_pencils.html}}</ref> 这些铅笔经常被人带走，在韩国的耗损率尤其高。<ref name="澎湃新闻">{{Cite news|url = http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1303681|title = 韩国宜家免费铅笔两年的供应量，两个月内被“顺”光 = 澎湃新闻|date = 13 February 2015|accessdate = 15 September 2015|author = 方晓|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304135232/http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1303681}}</ref>但宜家家居一名管理人员表示：“我们不太在意铅笔，用完了我们就会放上新的。”<ref>{{Cite news|title = IKEA Pencils Test Koreans’ Civility|url = http://koreabizwire.com/ikea-pencils-test-koreans-civility/30158|accessdate = 10 June 2015|work = KoreaBizWire|date = February 13, 2015|archive-date = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130603/http://koreabizwire.com/ikea-pencils-test-koreans-civility/30158}}</ref>

宜家家居并不反对宜家铅笔被使用在其他场合，因此也出现过一些手创或艺术品。例如，荷兰艺术家 Judith Delleman 曾经使用数百支宜家铅笔制作了一把椅子。<ref name="Toronto Star">{{Cite news|url = http://www.thestar.com/life/2010/12/22/a_penchant_for_pencils.html|title = A penchant for pencils|work = [[Toronto_Star|Toronto Star]]|date = 22 December 2010|accessdate = 11 November 2014|author = Cross, Allison}}</ref>

